OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777136757
OL,3,CHMS Prince of Wales prepares for
OL,4,CArctic deployment to 'protect UK
OL,5,Cwaters'
OL,7,FThe aircraft carrier HMS Prince of
OL,8,FWales has left Portsmouth harbour in
OL,9,Fpreparation for a deployment in the
OL,10,FArctic to "protect UK waters", the
OL,11,FRoyal Navy said.
OL,13,FThe Royal Navy flagship and its crew
OL,14,Fof more than 900 sailed from the naval
OL,15,Fbase on Friday carrying helicopters
OL,16,Fand drones.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@]O]
