PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777136757
OL,3,CHMS Prince of Wales prepares for
OL,4,CArctic deployment to 'protect UK
OL,5,Cwaters'
OL,7,FThe warship will deploy to the High
OL,8,FNorth and North Atlantic later this
OL,9,Fyear and take part in operations under
OL,10,FNato's Arctic Sentry mission ` the
OL,11,Falliance's initiative to improve
OL,12,Fsecurity in the region.
OL,14,FIt comes after the UK and allies
OL,15,Ftracked a Russian attack submarine and
OL,16,Ftwo spy submarines loitering near
OL,17,Fcritical undersea infrastructure in
OL,18,Fthe High North last month.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
