OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777136757
OL,3,CHMS Prince of Wales prepares for
OL,4,CArctic deployment to 'protect UK
OL,5,Cwaters'
OL,7,F"The High North continues to be a
OL,8,Fcritical area of interest to the Royal
OL,9,FNavy with regular deployments to the
OL,10,FArctic Circle and surrounding areas `
OL,11,Fworking alongside allies and
OL,12,Fpartners," the Royal Navy said in a
OL,13,Fstatement on Friday."
OL,15,FIt comes as the Royal Navy and the
OL,16,Fwider UK armed forces continue to be
OL,17,Fready to protect UK waters and wider
OL,18,Finterests from a variety of potential
OL,19,Fthreats.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]uD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
