PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777136757
OL,3,CHMS Prince of Wales prepares for
OL,4,CArctic deployment to 'protect UK
OL,5,Cwaters'
OL,7,F"The ship will undergo training in UK
OL,8,Fwaters before the ship embarks
OL,9,Fammunition in Scotland ready for
OL,10,Foperations, according to the Royal
OL,11,FNavy.
OL,13,FHMS Prince of Wales had been in
OL,14,FPortsmouth Naval Base since the end of
OL,15,FNovember, when it completed an eight-
OL,16,Fmonth mission to the western Indo-
OL,17,FPacific region.
OL,26,@oD@AO]
