PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777136757
OL,3,CHMS Prince of Wales prepares for
OL,4,CArctic deployment to 'protect UK
OL,5,Cwaters'
OL,7,FEarlier this month, Defence Secretary
OL,8,FJohn Healey said the Russian activity
OL,9,Fin UK waters was closely monitored and
OL,10,Fwarned Russia that any attempt to
OL,11,Fdamage infrastructure would have
OL,12,F"serious consequences".
OL,14,FAddressing Russian President Vladimir
OL,15,FPutin, Mr Healey said: "We see your
OL,16,Factivity over our cables and our
OL,17,Fpipelines, and you should know that
OL,18,Fany attempt to damage them will not be
OL,19,Ftolerated and will have serious
OL,20,Fconsequences."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@VO]wD@XOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
