OL,3,CHMS Prince of Wales prepares for
OL,4,CArctic deployment to 'protect UK
OL,5,Cwaters'
OL,7,FHe added that ` while many eyes were
OL,8,Ftrained on the Middle East crisis `
OL,9,Fthe UK, in partnership with Norway and
OL,10,Fother allies, responded to "increased
OL,11,FRussian activity" in the Atlantic
OL,12,Fnorth of the UK.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
